{
  "stem": "27335.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they were waiting for us already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there too, there were only were orange juice to drink.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when I-- I was sitting here on this side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Adam is next to me, and all the rest around it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And right across from there, there was another [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And right beside him, it-- Hannah was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we just kept-- kept looking at each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then after-- after the few-- we exchanged about how we like Cairo, what-- what we had learned, coming so far away, land [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we told them we enjoy it very much, and we are overwhelmed with the-- with the tropical, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So idle talk, you see?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, somebody started to sing in Hungarian, a rebel [HUNGARIAN] song that you could only sing underground or in isolated place where no [NON-ENGLISH]-- well, never about a [NON-ENGLISH], but nobody will-- [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's about Hungarian Red Army from the 1919, a song of the Red Army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he looked at Adam, and he looked back at-- at me, by Christ.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they came to the [HUNGARIAN], so we just got in with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they looked at [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's how it-- that's how it happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a test.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were prepared for it with-- we had to-- we have to test them out, if they-- they-- they-- they really are what we think they are.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And no, no, no questions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sang the song right through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Full-- with full--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With full-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With full lung and so on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we ended-- ended with the song, well-- well, we just melted together, you see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- Did Hannah sing too?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
